---
description: Agent OS routing rule (thin shim)
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

1) Read root `AGENTS.md` first.
2) Then read `project/BOARD.md`.
3) Then read the assigned/active task file in `project/tasks/`.
4) Read `project/PRD.md` and `project/workflows/*` only when needed.
5) If no active task exists, follow task selection and creation rules in `AGENTS.md`.